'''Mo'andas Karamchan Giandi''', nuo az '''Mohandas Karamchand Gandhi''' ([[Gujarati|Gujarati]]: '''મોહનદાસ કરમચંદ ગાંધી'''; 2 Aktuoba 1869 – 30 Janiweri 1948) wehna di prii-''h''eminent palitikal ahn pirichual liida a ''h''India juurin di ''h''Indian indipendans muuvment. Ihn wehna di payanier a ''satyagraha''—rizistans tu tirani chuu mas sibl disabiidians, foun chrang-chrang pahn ''ahimsa'' ar tuotal nan-vailens—ush kyaa ''h''India tu indipendans ahn inspaya muuvment fi sibl rait ahn friidam kraas di wol. Giandi  kamanli nuo rong di wol az Ma'atma Giandi ([[Sanskrit|Sanskrit]]: महात्मा mahātmā ar ''Griet Suol'', di anarifik fos aplai tu im bai Rabinjranat Taguor ([[Rabindranath Tagore|Rabindranath Tagore]]), ahn ina ''h''India alzwel az ''Bapu'' (Gujarati: બાપુ bāpu ar 'Faada'). Ihn ofishal ana ina ''h''India az di Faada a di Nieshan; ihn botdie, 2 Aktuoba, kamemariet de az Giandi Jayanti, a nashinal alidie, ahn woldwaid az di Intanashinal Die a Nan-Vailens.

